Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
130 Commercial Road is a 4 storey commercial building positioned in the
heart of Teneriffe. Built in the early 1900's and immaculately refurbished
in 2002, the building provides approximately 4,338 sqm of office and
retail accommodation. The property is leased to a range of national and
international tenants occupying full and part floor tenancies.

130 Commercial Road is an iconic building within the Teneriffe precinct.
